{"tid":2233951,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國副總統候選人電視辯論將於本港時間星期四早上上演","createTime":"2020-10-07T13:34:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T02:05:06.000Z","uid":44209,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a0f2429653ca3a0703dc26209f6cdec5fa0d47ff","tid":2233951,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T13:34:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BKgwZ7V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBKgwZ7V.jpg&h=53d12aa0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/rthk_new_c/135487\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frthk_new_c%2F135487&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmcVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=8c4a9267\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/rthk_new_c/135487</a><br />\n彭斯和賀錦麗將隔著玻璃進行副總統候選人電視辯論<br />\n<br />\n美國大選唯一一場副總統候選人電視辯論，在本港時間星期四早上上演，現任副總統彭斯與民主黨的賀錦麗同台較量。鑑於白宮有多人確診，兩人將隔著玻璃辯論。使用玻璃分隔是民主黨競選團隊提出，總統辯論委員會採納，但據報彭斯團隊一度反對，但一名幕僚之後說，認同措施在科學上有必要。辯論在猶他州鹽湖城的猶他大學舉行，大學將抽籤，讓少於100名學生入場，他們會保持距離，也必須戴口罩。辯論將分為9個環節，每節10分鐘。暫時未知辯論主題，但新型肺炎很可能是焦點，特別是總統特朗普確診、彭斯又是白宮抗疫工作小組負責人，他要向外界就政府的防疫工作辯護。<br />\n<br />\n2020-10-07 21:11:40"},{"pid":"bd3aca9db3ff73739729ebc45b99f87115ba47c1","tid":2233951,"uid":61005,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T13:37:43.000Z","msg":"鷹眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個眼神有殺氣到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"107994341a88858b441466ea225dce2794fea0f2","tid":2233951,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T13:38:06.000Z","msg":"會唔會俾個八婆蝦"},{"pid":"5cafee4ff6a2c02479c5379e71531515d5cb70c2","tid":2233951,"uid":284039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T13:38:20.000Z","msg":"早上即係幾點"},{"pid":"c57eae9fefdd1cd012ce5c3a5e87dc8c10fd0f1f","tid":2233951,"uid":325346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5cafee4ff6a2c02479c5379e71531515d5cb70c2","tid":2233951,"uid":284039,"like":0,"dislik